      • write

        public long write(Set<UUID> streamIDs,
                  Object object)
        Write an object to multiple streams, retuning the physical address it was written at.

        Note: While the completion of this operation guarantees that the append has been persisted, it DOES NOT guarantee that the object has been written to the stream. For example, another client may have deleted the stream.

        Parameters:
        object - The object to append to the stream.
        Returns:
        The address this
